  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink18-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">
          parattaiyiṉ pirintuvantu teḷittuk kūṭiya talaimakaṟkup piṉ avvoḻukkam uḷatāyavaḻi avaṉ varaviṭutta vāyilkaṭkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
          </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink18">
        <lg type="edition">
<l>          iruñcā yaṉṉa ceruntiyoṭu vēḻaṅ</l>
<l>          karumpi ṉalamaruṅ kaḻaṉi yūraṉ</l>
<l>          poruntumala raṉṉaveṉ kaṇṇaḻap</l>
<l>          pirintaṉa ṉallaṉō piriyale ṉeṉṟē.</l>


        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

<l>          The man from the village with fields where wild cane </l>
<l>          with dark, sedge-like pear trees whirls amongst the sugarcane–</l>
<l>          After saying 'I shan't leave [you],' he left [me], didn't he? </l>
<l>          So my eyes like matching blossoms cry. </l>
          


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
